From: Scott Boudreaux <scott@elyanlabs.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 2025
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] Add ppc64le to Python wheel platform list

Adds PowerPC 64-bit little-endian to the list of supported platforms
for the Python bindings wheel build.

---
 hailort/libhailort/bindings/python/platform/setup.py | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/hailort/libhailort/bindings/python/platform/setup.py b/hailort/libhailort/bindings/python/platform/setup.py
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/hailort/libhailort/bindings/python/platform/setup.py
+++ b/hailort/libhailort/bindings/python/platform/setup.py
@@ -255,6 +255,7 @@ if __name__ == "__main__":
         platforms=[
             "linux_x86_64",
             "linux_aarch64",
+            "linux_ppc64le",
         ],
         url="https://hailo.ai/",
         version="5.2.0",
--
2.39.0
